Tool.Notes:
Subject Copy copies selected subjects and all related data from a site within the source study environment to a site within the target study environment. Note: To copy a large number of subjects, use the Site Copy script.
1. Select a Source Site from the list of available sites. On selection, a list of target sites and a list of subjects to copy will appear. 2. Select a Target Site. Note: The script will not copy to a PROD target site. 3. Select Subjects to Copy from the list of subjects in the source site. Use Ctrl. or Shift to select multiple subjects. 4. Click Execute to copy the selected subjects to the target site.
